  "title": "Regional Sales Manager #75446",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Home Appliance</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Regional Sales Manager</strong></li><li>Working Location: Ubi Road</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Mon – Fri, 9.00am – 6.00PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic salary up to $4,500 + Commission + Transport Allowance + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Lead and oversee a team of sales promoters</li><li>Develop and implement sales strategies with the marketing team</li><li>Participate in monthly sales and order planning meetings</li><li>Support brand and product promotion</li><li>Build and maintain strong relationships with dealers and trade partners</li><li>Set, manage, and monitor sales targets for dealers and trade partners</li><li>Achieve monthly and yearly sales goals set by the company</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in business management or related field</li><li>At least 2-3 years of sales experience in B2B and B2C, preferably in the home appliances industry</li><li>Proven sales track record</li><li>Strong negotiation and problem-solving skills</li><li>Valid Class 3 Driver’s license and access to a vehicle</li><li>Willing to travel overseas (Multiple times a year)</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#75446 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
